    <div class="container">
      <h1>Rental Guidelines</h1>
      <p>Thank you for choosing EquiSource. To ensure a smooth and hassle-free rental experience, please follow our guidelines below:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accurate Information:</strong> Please provide your real name and a valid phone number. This helps us contact you easily and ensures a seamless rental process.</li>
